        </item>
        <item>
            <title>重遊地鐵舊觀塘綫過海路段  《穿越鐵路秘景》第二集揭示路段仍有不斷維修</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/20/mtr-45th-2/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=mtr-45th-2</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/20/mtr-45th-2/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Wed, 20 Nov 2024 07:45:48 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港鐵]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港鐵 45 週年]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[港鐵 45 週年活動]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[穿越鐵路秘景]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1276155</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">港鐵公司今日再發佈《穿越鐵路秘景》系列第二集，帶大家重遊舊觀塘綫過海，由藍田站出發，進入舊觀塘綫路段，再穿越東區海底隧道鐵路段，最後直達鰂魚湧站，在港鐵為慶祝與香港連繫相伴 45 載之際，一起重温九十年代從觀塘綫直接過海的集體回憶。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_57452"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/q5BKa4qXEX8?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="text-align: center;">▲穿越鐵路秘景 &#8211; 重遊舊觀塘綫過海</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>舊觀塘綫路段：昔日觀塘綫改道的城市規劃印記</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">隨着東區海底隧道啟用，觀塘綫於一九八九年經東隧伸延至港島鰂魚湧站，直至二零零二年將軍澳綫正式投入服務，觀塘綫改道以調景嶺為終點站。而由藍田站至現行將軍澳綫交匯處，便成為今日的舊觀塘綫路段，全長約 880 米，日常載客列車從此不再駛經，舊路段現時主要保留作車長駕駛訓練及讓工程車行駛至各市區綫車站進行維修工作。作為港鐵歷史最悠久的市區鐵路綫，觀塘綫在過去 45 年中見證了城市規劃的演變與發展歷程。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276156 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080458-694x483.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="483" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080458-694x483.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080458-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲觀塘綫於一九八九年經東隧伸延至港島鰂魚湧站（圖片來源：港鐵新聞稿）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276157 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2002-499x580.jpg" alt="" width="499" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2002-499x580.jpg 499w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2002.jpg 774w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 499px" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400; text-align: center;">▲直至二零零二年將軍澳綫正式投入服務（圖片來源：港鐵新聞稿）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276158 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080550-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080550-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/unwire-1732080550-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲觀塘綫改道以調景嶺為終點站（圖片來源：港鐵新聞稿）</p><h2 style="font-weight: 400;"><strong>茶果嶺露天段</strong><strong>：重遇東隧收費廣場前的景緻</strong></h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">在舊觀塘綫路段的中段位置，就是茶果嶺露天段，它位於東區海底隧道收費廣場巴士站旁，昔日的乘客途經此處可一覽車外景色。隨後便進入舊路段與現行將軍澳綫交匯處，然後進入東區海底隧道，最後直抵鰂魚湧站。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276159 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1-1-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1-1-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/1-1-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276161 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/2-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲茶果嶺露天段（圖片來源：港鐵新聞稿）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1276160 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241120at-694x461.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="461" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241120at-694x461.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/screenshot20241120at.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲舊路段與現行將軍澳綫交匯處（圖片來源：港鐵新聞稿）</p><p style="font-weight: 400;"><strong></strong></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/11/20/mtr-45th-2/life-tech/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
